   494→#### DAL-002: Virtual Device Lab & Keyboard Driver
   495→**Points: 4 | Priority: High**
   496→
   497→**Description:** Build the virtual device simulation environment and implement the first real device driver.
   498→
   499→**Technical Requirements:**
   500→- Virtual devices that simulate real hardware behavior
   501→- Configurable response patterns and timing characteristics
   502→- Integration with time-travel simulator for predictable testing
   503→- Reference keyboard driver implementation
   504→- Device testing framework for validation
   505→
   506→**Acceptance Criteria:**
   507→- [ ] Virtual keyboard provides realistic key press simulation
   508→- [ ] Virtual response box simulates button timing and lighting
   509→- [ ] Virtual eye tracker generates realistic gaze patterns
