- [ ] Timing validation confirms experimental precision

**Target Paradigms (First 10):**
1. **Stroop Color-Word Interference** ✅ (implemented above)
2. **Flanker Task (Eriksen & Eriksen, 1974)**
3. **Simon Task (Simon & Wolf, 1963)**
4. **Posner Spatial Cueing (Posner, 1980)**
5. **Go/No-Go Response Inhibition**
6. **Stop Signal Task (Logan & Cowan, 1984)**
7. **N-Back Working Memory (Kirchner, 1958)**
8. **Oddball ERP Paradigm (Squires et al., 1975)**
